<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Draft Entry</div>
<dl id="pC0d"><dt>III&sect;<a href="../../flex/p/pc0d.htm">1B.0/1C.0</a> </dt> <dd>First draft (pencil) of &ldquo;The Ondt and the Gracehoper&rdquo;, in a small pink notebook; probably February 1928, sent to Harriet Shaw Weaver 20 March 1928 (see Selected Letters, <a name="26Mar1928" href="../../ff/fbiog/fwlett.htm#26Mar1928">26 March</a>, and III, <a name="28Mar1928" href="../../ff/fbiog/fwlett.htm#28Mar1928">28 March</a>, 1928). <ul><li>MS: BL 47483, fols. 81r, / (81r), 82r, 83r, 83v-84r 84v-85r, 86r, 86v-87r, 87v-88r, 88v-89r </li><li>JJA 57 (Book III Chapters 1 and 2): 293-307 </li><li>Notebooks used: <a name="n29" href="../../ff/fdra/fnbdetails.htm#n29">N29 (VI.B.21)</a> (up to p. 200) </li></ul> </dd> </dl>
